 2041, \"to\": 2063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Hughes is keen to get his hands on the historic item and give it to his father.\", \"from\": 2067, \"to\": 2155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2076, \"end\": 2082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"score\": 0.997182907042069, \"rank\": 0.002812851459560675, \"text\": \"Hughes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Howard_Hughes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his hands\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"the historic item\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I would not even want it for myself.\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd want it for my dad.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2218, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know he'd just love, love having it,' he added.\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'When I look back in time in my career, I do not collect too many things for myself, but my dad's a monster collector for the three of us.\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2295}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"too many things\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2342}, {\"ngram\": \"my dad\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"a monster collector\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know he would have a special place for it.'\", \"from\": 2409, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a special place\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite his protests, Hughes faces a